# 📊 Motorola Sales Dashboard (Power BI)

## 📌 Project Overview
This project analyzes mobile sales performance across cities, brands, and time using Power BI.

## 📊 Key Metrics
- Total Sales: 769.20M
- Total Quantity: 19K
- Total Transactions: 4K
- Average Price: 40.11K

## 📈 Dashboard Insights
- Sales trends vary across months with peaks in March & July
- Apple and Samsung lead in total sales
- UPI is the most used payment method
- Weekend sales (Saturday) are highest

